msgid "Union (multiple)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:1140
msgid ""
"Multiple overlay layers can also be used, in which case features from "
"each layer are split at their overlap with features from all other "
"layers, creating a layer containing all the portions from both input and "
"overlay layers. Features on the same layer will not split each other. The"
